unknown_3: Senpai, new events are begun, hurry up to finish them!
contents_1: Senpai, new events are begun, hurry up to finish them!
contents_4: 學長大大，新的活動開始了，抓緊時間完成吧！
contents_5: 先輩、新しいイベントが始まりました、さっそく参加しましょう！
contents_2: Senpai, des nouveaux événements ont commencés, dépêche-toi de les finir !

unknown_3: Senpai, don’t miss your daily mission~
contents_1: Senpai, don’t miss your daily mission~
contents_4: 日常測驗還未完成，學長大大不要錯過啊！
contents_5: 日常テストはまだクリアしてませんよ、クリアを忘れずに！
contents_2: Senpai! N'oublie pas tes missions quotidiennes~

unknown_3: Senpai, come to see new change in campus!
contents_1: Senpai, come to see new change in campus!
contents_4: 學長大大，校園世界有了新的變化，快回來看看吧！
contents_5: 先輩、学園にいろんな変化が起こりましたよ！早速確認しましょう！
contents_2: Senpai, viens voir les changements sur le campus !

unknown_3: Senpai, your girls are miss you badly, hurry back!
contents_1: Senpai, your girls are miss you badly, hurry back!
contents_4: 學長大大，您的戰姬十分想念您，快回來看看吧！
contents_5: 先輩、戦姫が待っていますよ！早く戻ってきてくださいね！
contents_2: Senpai! Tu manques terriblement à tes Filles, reviens vite !

unknown_3: Senpai, your girls cannot fight without you, hurry back~
contents_1: Senpai, your girls cannot fight without you, hurry back~
contents_4: 學長大大，戰姬們沒有您的指揮實力大降，快回來和她們共同戰鬥吧！
contents_5: 先輩がいなければ、戦姫たちの戦闘力が大幅に下がってしまいます。早く戻って共に戦いましょう！
contents_2: Senpai, vos Filles ne peuvent pas se battre sans toi, reviens~

unknown_3: Senpai, campus will be full of devils if you don’t come back!
contents_1: Senpai, campus will be full of devils if you don’t come back!
contents_4: 學長大大，您再不回來，學園就要被惡魔學園佔領了！
contents_5: 先輩、早く戻らないと、学園は悪魔に占領されてしまいますよ！
contents_2: Senpai, le campus va être rempli de démon si tu ne reviens pas !

unknown_3: Senpai, you truly want to abandon your battle girls?
contents_1: Senpai, you truly want to abandon your battle girls?
contents_4: 學長大大，您不回來了嗎？您真的不要您的戰姬了嗎？
contents_5: 先輩は戻ってこないのですか？戦姫たちはいつでも先輩を待っています。
contents_2: Senpai, veux-tu vraiment abandonner tes Filles?

unknown_3: Senpai, you have uninitiated internship task, hurry to finish!
contents_1: Senpai, you have uninitiated internship task, hurry to finish!
contents_4: 學長大大，您還有未進行的打工任務，快派出戰姬去完成吧！
contents_5: 先輩、開始していないバイトミッションがありますよ、早く戦姫たちを派遣しましょう！
contents_2: Senpai, tu n'as pas commencé de tâche de stage, dépêche toi d'y aller

unknown_3: Senpai! Your team was defeated in campus league! Revenge now!
contents_1: Senpai, your rank in Campus League is declined, time to check out!
contents_4: 學長大大，您在校園聯賽中的隊伍被擊敗了，快回來復仇吧！
contents_5: 先輩、学園リーグのチームが敗北しました、早くリベンジしましょう！
contents_2: Senpai ! Your team was defeated in campus league! Revenge now!

unknown_3: Guild Notice changed: {1}
contents_1: Guild Notice changed: {1}
contents_4: 公會公告修改為：{1}
contents_5: サークルお知らせは次のように変更されました：{1}
contents_2: Guild Notice changed: {1}

unknown_3: Leader! We need your help of building guild! Come back!
contents_1: Leader! We need your help of building guild! Come back!
contents_4: 社長大大，公會的發展出了一些問題，快回來解決吧！
contents_5: 部長、サークルにちょっと問題があったようです、早く戻って解決しましょう！
contents_2: Leader! We need your help of building guild! Reviens !

unknown_3: Leader! Our guild can't move on without you! Please come back!
contents_1: Leader! Our guild can't move on without you! Please come back!
contents_4: 社長大大，公會的發展離不開您的領導，快回來吧！
contents_5: 部長、サークルには部長の指導が必要です！早く戻ってください！
contents_2: Leader! Our guild can't move on without you! Please come back!

unknown_3: Leader! Where are you? We have something serous happened in guild!
contents_1: Leader! Where are you? We have something serous happened in guild!
contents_4: 社長大大，在您離開的這段時間，幫會的發展大不如前，快回來主持大局吧！
contents_5: 部長がいない間、サークルの発展は上手くできませんでした。早く戻ってください！
contents_2: Leader! Where are you? We have something serous happened in guild!

unknown_3: Leader! Do you really want to leave your guild? Please come back!
contents_1: Leader! Do you really want to leave your guild? Please come back!
contents_4: 社長大大，您真的不要您的工會和您的同學了嗎？
contents_5: 部長、サークルの皆とクラスメイト達があなたを待っていますよ。
contents_2: Leader! Do you really want to leave your guild? Please come back!

unknown_3: Senpai! How was your first day in campus? Was it great?
contents_1: Senpai! How was your first day in campus? Was it great?
contents_4: 學長大大，校園生活第一天感覺如何呀？是不是很輕鬆愜意呢！
contents_5: 先輩、学園生活はどうですか？のんびりしているでしょう！
contents_2: Senpai! How was your first day in campus? Was it great?

unknown_3: Senpai! Girls were all talking about you these days!
contents_1: Senpai! Girls were all talking about you these days!
contents_4: 學長大大，經過兩天的相處，您的戰姬都夸您是位很好的學長呢！
contents_5: 先輩、この二日間の付き合いで、戦姫にいい先輩だと褒められました！
contents_2: Senpai! Girls were all talking about you these days!

unknown_3: Senpai! You and your girls are working better and better! Fight!
contents_1: Senpai! You and your girls are working better and better! Fight!
contents_4: 學長大大，您和戰姬們的配合越來越熟練了呢，繼續加油吧！
contents_5: 先輩、戦姫達との相性がよくなりましたね！引き続き頑張りましょう！
contents_2: Senpai! You and your girls are working better and better! Fight!

unknown_3: Senpai! You are the chosen one to help us defeat demons!
contents_1: Senpai! You are the chosen one to help us defeat demons!
contents_4: 學長大大，在您的幫助下，惡魔學園節節敗退，真不愧為被選召之人！
contents_5: 先輩のお陰で、悪魔学園を倒すことができました。さすが選ばれた人は違いますね！
contents_2: Senpai! You are the chosen one to help us defeat demons!

unknown_3: Senpai! Many girls are sending your letters! Come and see!
contents_1: Senpai! Many girls are sending your letters! Come and see!
contents_4: 學長大大，有許多戰姬在私下對您表露芳心了呢，以後和她們好好相處吧！
contents_5: 先輩、あなたのことが好きな戦姫がたくさんいますよ！仲良くしましょう！
contents_2: Senpai! Many girls are sending your letters! Come and see!

unknown_3: Senpai! Please select your orders in Canteen!
contents_1: Senpai! Please select your orders in Canteen!
contents_4: 學長大大，您好像忘記今天的食堂訂單了呦，快去完成訂單吧！
contents_5: 先輩、今日の食堂の注文を忘れたようですね。早く作りましょう！
contents_2: Senpai! Please select your orders in Canteen!

unknown_3: Senpai! You still have boss fight in guild! Come join the fight!
contents_1: Senpai! You still have boss fight in guild! Come join the fight!
contents_4: 學長大大，您今天還未挑戰公會副本呢，快來參加戰鬥吧！
contents_5: 先輩、今日はまだサークルクエストに挑戦していないようですね。早く参戦しましょう！
contents_2: Senpai! You still have boss fight in guild! Come join the fight!

unknown_3: You have advanced to the next phase in Ultimate League! Don't forget to set up your Defense Lineup!
contents_1: You have advanced to the next phase in Ultimate League! Don't forget to set up your Defense Lineup!
contents_4: 恭喜學長大大終極聯賽成功晉級，快來設置防守陣容把！
contents_5: おめでとうございます！インフィニティリーグの予選を突破しました！今すぐ防衛設定を行いましょう！
contents_2: La phase Ruée de Points dans l'Arène Ultime va bientôt prendre fin ! C'est votre dernière chance pour y participer, Senpai !

unknown_3: Points Race of Ultimate League will end soon! Now is the last chance to participate!
contents_1: Points Race of Ultimate League will end soon! Now is the last chance to participate!
contents_4: 學長大大，終極聯賽積分賽即將結束，快來參加戰鬥吧！
contents_5: 先輩！インフィニティリーグポイント戦が間もなく終了します！今すぐ参加しましょう！
contents_2: Vous êtes arrivé(e) à la phase suivante dans l'Arène Ultime ! N'oubliez pas former votre équipe défensive, Senpai~
